Author: Huangyi Tang [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Huangyi Tang <tang749@purdue.edu>
Description: Pedigree quality control (duplicates, loops, sex mismatch, birth order),
    fixing (remove invalid links, break loops), inbreeding coefficient (F) and
    ancestor contribution. Supports vectors, data frames and file input.
    Uses Rcpp for performance.
